{
  "name": "Crumbl Base Protein Cookie",
  "description": "Flavor-neutral champion base for the crumbl protein-cookie family, synthesized from the set: Birthday Cake (excellent) contributes the soft-crumb cornstarch trick + the inline yogurt/Cool-Whip frosting + the lean chassis; Lemon (excellent) corroborates cornstarch; the 20g Protein Frosted newcomer contributes the protein-loading lever (dialed to a measured 2 scoops, not its texture-risky 3-in-5) and the lean egg white for structure. Vanilla-only — no almond extract / sprinkles / lemon / cocoa, so flavors derive cleanly off it. Cornstarch and egg white are NOT authored here; they are grafted in via promote so the lineage records where each winning component came from. Sweetener is granulated Splenda. Not yet made.",
  "tags": [
